query_tattooable

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_tattooable -  This method queries whether or not the specified bodypart is tattooable or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_tattooable(string part)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^part%^RESET%^ - the name of the bodypart
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the bodypart is tattooable, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/effects/other/tattoo.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method queries whether or not the specified bodypart is
tattooable or not.
